docs {
  Call the Payments API to authorize payments, capture authorized payments, refund payments that have already been captured, and show payment information. Use the Payments API in conjunction with the <a href="https://developer.paypal.com/api/orders/v2/">Orders API</a>. For more information, see the <a href="https://developer.paypal.com/docs/checkout/">PayPal Checkout Overview</a>.
}
